{"title_page": "Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!", "text_new": "{{refimprove|date=February 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox animanga/Header\n| name            = \"Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!\"\n| image           = Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!.jpg\n| caption         =Featuring the main characters.\n| ja_kanji        = \u793e\u9577\u3001\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u6642\u9593\u3067\u3059\uff01\n| ja_romaji       = Shach\u014d, Batoru no Jikan Desu!\n| genre           = [[Action game|Action]], [[Adventure]],  [[Fantasy]]\n}}\n{{Infobox animanga/Game\n| developer       = Deluxe Games, Preapp Partners\n| publisher       = [[Kadokawa Corporation|Kadokawa Games]]\n| genre           = [[Role-playing game]]\n| platforms       = [[Android (operating system)|Android]], [[iOS]]\n| released        = {{Video game release|JP|October 17, 2019}}\n}}\n{{Infobox animanga/Video\n| type            = TV series\n| title           = \n| director        = Hiroki Ikeshita\n| producer        = \n| writer          = Kenta Ihara\n| music           = [[Yukari Hashimoto]]\n| studio          = [[C2C (studio)|C2C]]\n| licensee        = \n| network         = [[AT-X (TV network)|AT-X]], [[Tokyo MX]], [[Kyoto Broadcasting System|KBS Kyoto]], [[Sun Television|Sun TV]], BS NTV, [[TV Aichi]]\n| first           = April 5, 2020\n| last            = \n| episodes        = 12\n| episode_list    = \n}}\n{{Infobox animanga/Footer}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/images/encyc/A22910-2425874216.1584128569.jpg|title=A22910-2425874216.1584128569.jpg|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n'''{{Nihongo|\"Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!\"  |\u793e\u9577\u3001\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u6642\u9593\u3067\u3059\uff01|Shach\u014d, Batoru no Jikan Desu!|\"President, It's Time for Battle!\"}}''' is an online free-to-play [[role-playing game]] created by [[Kadokawa Corporation|Kadokawa]], Deluxe Games, and Preapp Partners. It was released in Japan on October 17, 2019 for [[Android (operating system)|Android]] and [[iOS]] devices. An [[anime]] television series adaptation by [[C2C (studio)|C2C]] premiered on April 5, 2020.\n\n==Characters==\n;{{nihongo|Minato|\u30df\u30ca\u30c8}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Shun Horie]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Yutoria|\u30e6\u30c8\u30ea\u30a2}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Kana Ichinose]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Akari|\u30a2\u30ab\u30ea}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Azumi Waki]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Makoto|\u30de\u30b3\u30c8}}\n:{{voiced by|Yoshino Aoyama<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Guide|\u30ac\u30a4\u30c9|Gaido}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Yui Horie]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Rivar|\u30e9\u30a4\u30d0\u30fc|Raib\u0101}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Taku Yashiro]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Valmi|\u30f4\u30a1\u30eb\u7f8e|Varumi}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Sumire Uesaka]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Subaru|\u30b9\u30d0\u30eb}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Himika Akaneya]]}}<ref name=\"staff-cast2\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-04/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-isekai-anime-2nd-promo-video-reveals-more-cast-song-artists/.157135|title='Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!' Isekai Anime's 2nd Promo Video Reveals More Cast, Song Artists|website=Anime News Network|language=en|access-date=2020-03-07}}</ref>\n:\n\n==Anime==\nAn [[anime]] television series adaptation was announced on December 1, 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-12-01/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-isekai-strategy-rpg-app-gets-tv-anime-in-2020/.153863|title=Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu! Isekai Strategy RPG App Gets TV Anime in 2020|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=December 1, 2019|accessdate=December 1, 2019}}</ref> The series is animated by [[C2C (studio)|C2C]] and directed by Hiroki Ikeshita, with Kenta Ihara handling series composition, Keisuke Watanabe designing the characters, and [[Yukari Hashimoto]] composing the series' music. It premiered on April 5, 2020.<ref name=\"staff-cast\">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-01-24/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-anime-video-reveals-cast-staff-april-premiere/.155749|title='Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!' Anime's Video Reveals Cast, Staff, April Premiere|website=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=January 24, 2020|date=January 24, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-02-25/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-anime-reveals-visual-april-5-premiere/.156828|title='Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!' Anime Reveals Visual, April 5 Premiere|website=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=February 26, 2020|date=February 25, 2020}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"plainrowheaders wikitable\" style=\"width:98%; margin:auto; background:#FFF;\"\n|- style=\"border-bottom: 3px solid #CCF;\"\n!{{Abbr|No.|Number}}\n! Title<ref>{{cite web|url=https://shachibato-anime.com/story.html|title=TV\u30a2\u30cb\u30e1\u300c\u793e\u9577\u3001\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u6642\u9593\u3067\u3059\uff01\u300d\u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8|accessdate=April 5, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n!Original air date\n|-\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 1\n| Title               = Becoming the President\n| TranslitTitle       = Shach\u014d sh\u016bnin\n| NativeTitle         = \u793e\u9577\u5c31\u4efb\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2020|4|5}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official website|https://shachibato.jp/|Game official website}} {{in lang|ja}}\n*{{Official website|https://shachibato-anime.com/|Anime official website}} {{in lang|ja}}\n*{{ann|anime|22910}}\n\n{{C2C (studio)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Shacho, Battle no Jikan Desu!}}\n[[Category:2019 video games]]\n[[Category:Android (operating system) games]]\n[[Category:Anime television series based on video games]]\n[[Category:C2C (studio)]]\n[[Category:Free-to-play video games]]\n[[Category:IOS games]]\n[[Category:Japan-exclusive video games]]\n[[Category:Japanese role-playing video games]]\n[[Category:Video games developed in Japan]]\n\n{{rpg-videogame-stub}}\n{{anime-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{refimprove|date=February 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox animanga/Header\n| name            = \"Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!\"\n| image           = Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!.jpg\n| caption         =Featuring the main characters.\n| ja_kanji        = \u793e\u9577\u3001\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u6642\u9593\u3067\u3059\uff01\n| ja_romaji       = Shach\u014d, Batoru no Jikan Desu!\n| genre           = [[Action]], [[Adventure]],  [[Fantasy]]\n}}\n{{Infobox animanga/Game\n| developer       = Deluxe Games, Preapp Partners\n| publisher       = [[Kadokawa Corporation|Kadokawa Games]]\n| genre           = [[Role-playing game]]\n| platforms       = [[Android (operating system)|Android]], [[iOS]]\n| released        = {{Video game release|JP|October 17, 2019}}\n}}\n{{Infobox animanga/Video\n| type            = TV series\n| title           = \n| director        = Hiroki Ikeshita\n| producer        = \n| writer          = Kenta Ihara\n| music           = [[Yukari Hashimoto]]\n| studio          = [[C2C (studio)|C2C]]\n| licensee        = \n| network         = [[AT-X (TV network)|AT-X]], [[Tokyo MX]], [[Kyoto Broadcasting System|KBS Kyoto]], [[Sun Television|Sun TV]], BS NTV, [[TV Aichi]]\n| first           = April 5, 2020\n| last            = \n| episodes        = 12\n| episode_list    = \n}}\n{{Infobox animanga/Footer}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/images/encyc/A22910-2425874216.1584128569.jpg|title=A22910-2425874216.1584128569.jpg|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n'''{{Nihongo|\"Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle!\"  |\u793e\u9577\u3001\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u6642\u9593\u3067\u3059\uff01|Shach\u014d, Batoru no Jikan Desu!|\"President, It's Time for Battle!\"}}''' is an online free-to-play [[role-playing game]] created by [[Kadokawa Corporation|Kadokawa]], Deluxe Games, and Preapp Partners. It was released in Japan on October 17, 2019 for [[Android (operating system)|Android]] and [[iOS]] devices. An [[anime]] television series adaptation by [[C2C (studio)|C2C]] premiered on April 5, 2020.\n\n==Characters==\n;{{nihongo|Minato|\u30df\u30ca\u30c8}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Shun Horie]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Yutoria|\u30e6\u30c8\u30ea\u30a2}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Kana Ichinose]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Akari|\u30a2\u30ab\u30ea}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Azumi Waki]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Makoto|\u30de\u30b3\u30c8}}\n:{{voiced by|Yoshino Aoyama<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Guide|\u30ac\u30a4\u30c9|Gaido}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Yui Horie]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Rivar|\u30e9\u30a4\u30d0\u30fc|Raib\u0101}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Taku Yashiro]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Valmi|\u30f4\u30a1\u30eb\u7f8e|Varumi}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Sumire Uesaka]]<ref name=\"staff-cast\"/>}}\n:\n;{{nihongo|Subaru|\u30b9\u30d0\u30eb}}\n:{{voiced by|[[Himika Akaneya]]}}<ref name=\"staff-cast2\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-03-04/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-isekai-anime-2nd-promo-video-reveals-more-cast-song-artists/.157135|title='Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!' Isekai Anime's 2nd Promo Video Reveals More Cast, Song Artists|website=Anime News Network|language=en|access-date=2020-03-07}}</ref>\n:\n\n==Anime==\nAn [[anime]] television series adaptation was announced on December 1, 2019.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2019-12-01/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-isekai-strategy-rpg-app-gets-tv-anime-in-2020/.153863|title=Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu! Isekai Strategy RPG App Gets TV Anime in 2020|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=December 1, 2019|accessdate=December 1, 2019}}</ref> The series is animated by [[C2C (studio)|C2C]] and directed by Hiroki Ikeshita, with Kenta Ihara handling series composition, Keisuke Watanabe designing the characters, and [[Yukari Hashimoto]] composing the series' music. It premiered on April 5, 2020.<ref name=\"staff-cast\">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-01-24/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-anime-video-reveals-cast-staff-april-premiere/.155749|title='Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!' Anime's Video Reveals Cast, Staff, April Premiere|website=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=January 24, 2020|date=January 24, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2020-02-25/shacho-battle-no-jikan-desu-anime-reveals-visual-april-5-premiere/.156828|title='Shach\u014d, Battle no Jikan Desu!' Anime Reveals Visual, April 5 Premiere|website=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=February 26, 2020|date=February 25, 2020}}</ref>\n\n{|class=\"plainrowheaders wikitable\" style=\"width:98%; margin:auto; background:#FFF;\"\n|- style=\"border-bottom: 3px solid #CCF;\"\n!{{Abbr|No.|Number}}\n! Title<ref>{{cite web|url=https://shachibato-anime.com/story.html|title=TV\u30a2\u30cb\u30e1\u300c\u793e\u9577\u3001\u30d0\u30c8\u30eb\u306e\u6642\u9593\u3067\u3059\uff01\u300d\u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8|accessdate=April 5, 2020|language=Japanese}}</ref>\n!Original air date\n|-\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 1\n| Title               = Becoming the President\n| TranslitTitle       = Shach\u014d sh\u016bnin\n| NativeTitle         = \u793e\u9577\u5c31\u4efb\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja\n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2020|4|5}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Official website|https://shachibato.jp/|Game official website}} {{in lang|ja}}\n*{{Official website|https://shachibato-anime.com/|Anime official website}} {{in lang|ja}}\n*{{ann|anime|22910}}\n\n{{C2C (studio)}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Shacho, Battle no Jikan Desu!}}\n[[Category:2019 video games]]\n[